The '''reclumi spider''' was an arthropod native to the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Null/Legends|Null]]. This species of [[Spider/Legends|spider]] could make a web strong enough to stop a moving vehicle.

In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], when the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] chased down the suspected [[Assassin/Legends|assassin]] that was thought to have murdered [[Samish Kash]], Anakin steered their borrowed [[Swoop/Legends|swoop]] into such a web, causing them to lose their suspect.

